<h2 style="font-size: 22px;">Watkins College of Art, Design &amp; Film</h2>
<strong>Nashville, TN</strong>

<div class="infolines">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers credit for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers placement into higher-level courses for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>


<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Students may earn college credit for acceptable scores from IB, CLEP and AP of the College Entrance Examination Board.  Credit-by-examination earns credit towards graduation to meet program requirements but carries no grade or quality points and is not used in the factoring of the GPA.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.watkins.edu/prospective-students/ap-clep-and-ib-credits" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

 <p class="box-padding-3">
    Additional restrictions and requirements may apply to the policy listed below. For more detailed information, visit the college's AP policy on the Web or contact the college directly.
 </p>

